## Background {.scrollable}

Economists and policymakers are interested in studying the potential determinants of economic growth and mechanisms through which the most significant benefit can be achieved.

Most countries that have aimed for sustained rapid growth have maintained impressive public investment rates in three key areas: infrastructure, education, and health. 

- To increase standards of living --- 

## Firm growth and economic growth

Two historical circumstances have indirectly inspired this research on broadening the understanding of the relationship between economic growth and firm growth. 

- firm growth and decline is at the core of economic dynamics.
- Firm growth provides “prosperity” and “opportunity”.

